reg_info.full_title: O. Reg. 111/12: ONTARIO LOCAL FOREST MANAGEMENT CORPORATIONS
reg_info.citation: O. Reg. 111/12: ONTARIO LOCAL FOREST MANAGEMENT CORPORATIONS

content.content: 1. An Ontario local forest management corporation to be known in English as the Nawiinginokiima Forest Management Corporation and in French as Société de gestion forestière Nawiinginokiima is established as a corporation without share capital.  O. Reg. 111/12, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1. An Ontario local forest management corporation to be known in English as the Nawiinginokiima Forest Management Corporation and in French as Société de gestion forestière Nawiinginokiima is established as a corporation without share capital.  O. Reg. 111/12, s. 1.

content.content: 1.1 An Ontario local forest management corporation to be known in English as the Temagami Forest Management Corporation and in French as Société de gestion forestière Temagami is established as a corporation without share capital. O. Reg. 750/20, s. 1.
content.raw_html: 1.1 An Ontario local forest management corporation to be known in English as the Temagami Forest Management Corporation and in French as Société de gestion forestière Temagami is established as a corporation without share capital. O. Reg. 750/20, s. 1.

content.content: 2. Omitted (provides for coming into force of provisions of this Regulation).  O. Reg. 111/12, s. 2.
